sp.p:
Not if old Daddy Bland knows it. Ladies, good morrow—the commandant and
officers of the fifty eighth give a ball at Elizabeth Castle to-morrow night;
truly it will lack brilliance if madame and yourself deny your company.

I heard the gentleman say something about murder; John, the waiter, says he's
very mysterious; I shall watch my gentleman, and give notice to the officers;
why shouldn't I get the reward as well as another?
